software:
gnuplot -- plotting software
feh -- image viewer
GNU make

make:
$ make build target=<name> -- to build <name> test (default value is 'shaker')
$ make plot target=<name> -- to plot <name> data (default value is 'shaker')
$ make run target=<name> -- to run <name> via 'time' (default value is 'shaker')

project structure:
./src/ -- source code files
./bin/ -- executables
./data/ -- benchmark data under .csv files, and plots under .png
